<!doctype html>
<html
  style="
  box-sizing: border-box;
    margin: 0;
    background-color: rgba(241, 245, 249, 1);
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  "
>
<head>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://rsms.me/" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://rsms.me/inter/inter.css" />
  <title>Byl jste odmítnut doktorem.</title>

  <style type="text/css">
      body {
          -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
          -webkit-text-size-adjust: none;
          width: 100% !important;
          height: 100%;
          line-height: 1.6em;
      }
      body {
          background-color: #f6f6f6;
      }
      body {
          padding: 0 !important;
          margin: 0 !important;
      }
      h1 {
          font-size: 20px !important;
          font-weight: 600 !important;
      }
      h2 {
          font-size: 18px !important;
          font-weight: 600 !important;
      }
      h3 {
          font-size: 16px !important;
      }
      h4 {
          font-size: 14px !important;
      }
      p {
          font-size: 12px !important;
      }
      span {
          font-size: 12px !important;
      }
      h1,
      h2,
      h3,
      h4,
      p,
      span {
          padding: 0;
          margin: 0;
          width: fit-content;
      }
      :root {
          font-family: roboto, sans-serif;
      }
      .inter-font {
          font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
          font-feature-settings:
                  'liga' 1,
                  'calt' 1;
      }
      .gradient-background {
          background: linear-gradient(
                  90deg,
                  rgba(245, 160, 1, 0.08) 1%,
                  rgba(59, 109, 209, 0.08) 100%
          );
      }
      .container {
          padding: 16px 24px;
      }
      .line {
          border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(211, 227, 243);
      }
      .bg-white {
          background-color: white;
      }
      .bg-offwhite {
          background-color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 255);
      }
      .bg-dark-blue {
          background-color: #012368;
      }
      .bg-darkest-blue {
          background-color: #0f172a;
      }
      .timeline-content-container {
          padding: 20px;
          border:rgb(211, 227, 243) 1px solid;
          border-radius: 8px;
          width: 100%;
      }
      .darkest-blue {
          color: #0f172a;
      }
      .dark-blue {
          color: #012368;
      }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
<div style="max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto">
  <div class="bg-offwhite container line" >
    <img
      style="height: 50px !important; width: auto !important;"
      src='https://www.ovladnimechyr.cz/email-logo.png',
      alt="UZIS logo"
      />
    <img
      style="height: 50px !important; width: auto !important;"
      src='https://www.ovladnimechyr.cz/email-logo-eu.png',
      alt="EU logo"
      />  </div>
  <div class="container bg-white">
    <h1 class="dark-blue inter-font">Dobrý den</h1>
    <h3 class="inter-font darkest-blue" style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400">
      <br />
      Doktor/doktorka <%= @doctor_name %> Vás odmítl/a.
      <br />
      Na <a href="<%= @doctors_url %>" target="_blank">seznamu doktorů</a> si můžete požádat o jiného lékaře.
      <br />
      <br />
      <br />
      <img
        style="height: 50px !important; width: auto !important;"
        src='https://www.ovladnimechyr.cz/email-logo.png',
        alt="UZIS logo"
        />
      <h4>Národní screeningové centrum</h4>
      Ústav zdravotnických informací a statistiky České republiky <br />
      Kounicova 688/26 <br />
      602 00 Brno <br />
      e-mail: <a href="mailto:podpora.nsc@uzis.cz">podpora.nsc@uzis.cz </a><br />
      <br />

      <h4>Informace o projektu poskytuje Helpdesk Národního screeningového centra</h4>
      Telefon: <a href="tel:+420770171533">+420 770 171 533</a>
    </h3>
  </div>

  <div class="container bg-white line" style="padding-bottom: 40px">
  </div>
  <div class="container bg-white">
    <p style="color: #334155">
      Na tuto zprávu neodpovídejte.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
